{"GYL53dbUwTm":{"id":"GYL53dbUwTm","type":"work","title":"兩漢博聞","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《兩漢博聞》•十二卷","summary":"明嘉靖中黃魯曾刊本。不著撰人名氏。案晁公武《讀書志》，乃宋楊侃所編也。侃，錢塘人，端拱中進士，官至集賢院學士。晚為知制誥，避真宗舊諱，更名大雅。是編摘錄前後《漢書》，不依篇第，不分門類。惟簡擇其字句故事列為標目，而節取顏師古及章懷太子《注》列於其下。凡《前漢書》七卷、《後漢書》五卷。雖於史學無關，然較他類書采摭雜說者，究為雅馴。《後漢書》中間有引及《前漢書》者，必標顏師古字。而所引梁劉昭《續漢志注》，乃與《章懷注》無別，體例未免少疏。至所列紀傳篇目，亦往往多有訛舛。然如《四皓》條下引《顏師古注》曰：“四皓稱號，本起於此，更無姓名可稱。蓋隱居之人，匿跡遠害，不自標顯，秘其氏族，故史傳無得而詳。至於皇甫謐、圈稱之徒及諸地理書說，竟為四人安姓字。自相錯互，語又不經。班氏不載於書，諸家皆臆說。今並棄略，一無取焉”云云。明監本《漢書注》竟佚此條，惟賴此書倖存，則亦非無資考證者矣。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"books":["CXVzss8cQWB"],"juan_count":{"number":12},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource-siku","name":"维基文库（四庫全書本）","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/兩漢博聞_(四庫全書本)","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=477829","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-sikuquanshuben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/SK0937","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"四庫全書本","version":"v4","total_page":782,"paragraph_count":2709,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-huanglucengmingjiaji","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ892411999015573117226","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"黃魯曾明嘉靖37年刻本","version":"v2","total_page":1003,"paragraph_count":4242,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-mingchaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ892411999013035114184","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"明抄本","version":"v2","total_page":746,"paragraph_count":6670,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dF9JBy":{"id":"GYL53dF9JBy","type":"work","title":"鹿洲公案","authors":[{"name":"藍鼎元","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《鹿洲公案》•二卷","author_info":"國朝藍鼎元撰","summary":"國朝藍鼎元撰。鼎元有《平臺紀略》，已著錄。此其知普甯縣時所讞諸案。自敍其推鞫始末，為二十四篇。","edition":"江西巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4522161","type":"text","details":"藍鼎元著"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=6591018","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=7733508","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-guangxuwuben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL01025148","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"光緒五年本","version":"v2","total_page":285,"paragraph_count":1526,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-congshujichengsanbia","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02119835","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"叢書集成三編","version":"v2","total_page":280,"paragraph_count":1106,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-jindaizhongguoshilia","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02026801","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"近代中國史料叢刊影印本","version":"v2","total_page":280,"paragraph_count":1023,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53d2uu7d":{"id":"GYL53d2uu7d","type":"work","title":"塞程別記","authors":[{"name":"餘寀","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《塞程別記》•一卷","author_info":"國朝餘寀撰","summary":"國朝餘寀撰。寀字同野，山陰人。其書記自京出古北口至喀爾倫一千五百餘裏。其時道路初開，未能有所考證。僅述風土氣候、山川草木之屬而已。","edition":"通行本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1}},"GYL53d81Utw":{"id":"GYL53d81Utw","type":"work","title":"滇遊記","authors":[{"name":"畢曰澪","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《滇遊記》•一卷、《附記》•一卷","author_info":"國朝畢曰澪撰","summary":"國朝畢曰澪撰。曰澪字秋岐，益都人，康熙中由貢生官任縣知縣。是編乃曰澪父忠谷官雲南布政司參議，曰澪省親時所作。案日記載道路見聞及旅中雜事，自三月十六日起，至十月十一日止。而《序》文及卷首俱不詳其為何年，殊嫌疏漏。考曰澪所作《蒼洱小記》，有孫寶文題詞。其《序》稱丙子臘日，曰澪邀飲，欲讀《滇記》云云。則作於康熙丙子以前也。其《附記》一卷，則途中所見土風，不可分系某日者，故總錄於末雲。","edition":"兵部侍郎紀昀家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"additional_works":[{"book_title":"附記","n_juan":1}],"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=744625","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-xuehaileibian","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CXHLB420","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"學海類編","version":"v4","total_page":33,"paragraph_count":52,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53duE6zT":{"id":"GYL53duE6zT","type":"work","title":"諸史提要","authors":[{"name":"錢端禮","role":"撰","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《諸史提要》•十五卷","author_info":"宋錢端禮撰","summary":"宋錢端禮撰。端禮字處和，臨安人，吳越王俶六世孫，榮國公忱之子。少以恩蔭入仕，累官至參知政事，兼權知樞密院事。以莊文太子妃父罷為資政殿太學士。再知甯國，移紹興，複以觀文殿學士提舉洞霄宮。卒諡忠肅。事蹟具《宋史》本傳。是書乃取諸史之文可資詞藻者，按部採摘，匯輯成編。各以一二語標題，而分注其首尾於下。凡《史記》一卷、《前漢書》二卷、《後漢書》二卷、《三國志》一卷、《晉書》三卷、《南史》一卷、《北史》一卷、《新唐書》三卷、《五代史》一卷。其著錄於《宋史•藝文志》者，與此本卷目相同。前有其門人劉孝韙《序》，不著年月。詳其詞意，蓋端禮為參政時所刊行也。其體例頗與洪邁《史漢法語》、《諸史精語》相近。陳振孫《書錄解題》嘗譏其泛然錄鈔，毫無義例。蓋南宋最尚詞科，以妃青儷白相高，故當時有此抄書之學也。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":15},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3994344","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-kangxiwushierwuyingd","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/SDZJ0664","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"康熙五十二年武英殿刊本","version":"v8","total_page":1051,"paragraph_count":1501,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02049562","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":1079,"paragraph_count":9367,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-kangxiwushierneifuke","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL06211853","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"康熙五十二年內府刻本","version":"v1","total_page":76,"paragraph_count":330,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dWzHmH":{"id":"GYL53dWzHmH","type":"work","title":"汪直傳","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《汪直傳》•一卷","author_info":"不著撰人名氏","summary":"不著撰人名氏。記嘉靖中汪直引倭入寇海上及總督胡宗憲以計誘殺直事。所以歸功於宗憲者甚至，或其幕客所為也。","edition":"戶部尚書王際華家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource-siku","name":"维基文库（四庫全書本）","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/汪直傳_(四庫全書本)","type":"text"}]},"GYL53dh3PmZ":{"id":"GYL53dh3PmZ","type":"work","title":"南史識小錄","authors":[{"name":"沈名蓀、朱昆田同","role":"編","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《南史識小錄》•八卷、《北史識小錄》•八卷","author_info":"國朝沈名蓀、朱昆田同編","summary":"國朝沈名蓀、朱昆田同編。名蓀字澗芳，錢塘人。昆田字文盎，秀水人，彝尊之子也。是書仿《兩漢博聞》之例，取《南北二史》，摘其字句之鮮華，事蹟之新異者，摘錄成編。不分門目，惟以原書次第臚列，而各著其篇名。亦不加訓釋，惟摘取數字標目，以原文載於其下，著是語之緣起而已。《文獻通考》載陳正敏之言曰：李延壽作《南北史》，粗得作史之體。故《唐書》本傳亦謂其刪略穢詞，過本書遠甚。然好述妖異兆祥謠讖，特為繁猥。又引司馬光之言，亦謂李延壽《書》於禨祥詼嘲小事，無所不載。蓋自沈約《宋書》以下，大抵競標藻采，務摭異聞，詞每涉乎儷裁，事或取諸小說。延壽因仍舊習，未盡湔除，宜為論者之所惜。然揆以史體，固曰稍乖，至於賦手取材，詩人隸事，則樵蘇漁獵，捃拾靡窮。此譬如柟瘤為病，而制枕者反貴其文理也。名蓀等擷其精華，以備選用，使遺文瑣事，披卷燦然。其書雖作自近人，其所採錄則皆唐以前事，與《藝文類聚》諸書約略相似。存以備考，愈於冗雜之類書多矣。","comment":"──右“史鈔類”三部、四十八卷，皆文淵閣著錄。","additional_comment":"○史鈔類存目","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"books":["CXVzssmPyS7"],"juan_count":{"number":8},"related_works":[{"id":"GYLt1Ei4Acf","title":"北史識小錄"}],"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=584909","type":"text"}]},"GYL53dmJcCo":{"id":"GYL53dmJcCo","type":"work","title":"南朝史精語","authors":[{"name":"洪邁","role":"撰","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《南朝史精語》•十卷","author_info":"宋洪邁撰","summary":"宋洪邁撰。邁於諸書多有節本。其所纂輯，自《經子》至《前漢》皆曰《法語》，自《後漢》至《唐書》皆曰《精語》。此所摘宋、齊、梁、陳四朝史中之語也。凡《宋書》四卷、《齊書》三卷、《梁書》二卷、《陳書》一卷。其去取多不可解。即以卷首《宋本紀》考之，如《桓玄與劉邁書》有雲：“北府人情雲何，近見劉雲何所道”，乃獨摘“北府人情雲何”句。《宋順帝反正詔》曰：“故順聲一唱，二溟卷波，英風振路，宸居清翳”，乃獨摘“二溟卷波”句。高祖北討，加領征將軍，司、豫二州刺史，以世子為徐、兗二州刺史，下書有雲：“今當奉辭西旆，有事關中，弱嗣叨蒙，複忝今授”，乃獨摘“複忝今授”四字。又如《加高祖九錫》策文，駢詞麗句，疊出不窮，乃獨摘“出藩入輔，鋒無前對”二句。蓋南宋最重詞科，士大夫多節錄古書，以備遣用。其排比成編者，則有王應麟《玉海》、章俊卿《山堂考索》之流。巾箱秘本，本非著書，不幸而為人所傳者，則有如此類。後人以其名重存之，實非其志也。以流傳已久，姑存其目，實則無可採錄。惟其中所錄《宋書》，《本紀》第一，《列傳》第二、第三，《志》第四，《志》反在《列傳》之後。考劉知幾《史通》曰：“舊史以《表》、《志》之帙，分於《紀》、《傳》之間。降及蔚宗，肇加厘革。沈、魏繼作，相與因循。今北監版《魏書》，《志》在《列傳》後，是其顯證，與《史通》合。而《宋書》則移其次第，列於《紀》、《傳》之間。觀邁所序，猶從古本。知幾之言不妄，是則可資考證之一端。十卷之中，惟此一節足取耳。","edition":"浙江汪啟淑家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=447492","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02049546","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":204,"paragraph_count":1859,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dyY1H9":{"id":"GYL53dyY1H9","type":"work","title":"元史節要","authors":[{"name":"張九韶","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《元史節要》•十四卷","author_info":"明張九韶撰","summary":"明張九韶撰。九韶字美和，清江人。洪武十年，以薦為國子助教，升翰林院編修。是編因當時所修《元史》版藏內府，人間多不得見。於是仿曾先之《十八史略》例，節其要為一書。其編年系事，則仍用《通鑒》之體。前有洪武甲子《自序》一篇。然紀載多不具首尾，未為該備。且此書成於洪武間，而《順帝紀》內多有稱“明太祖高皇帝”者，疑其經後人所改竄，非九韶原本也。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":14},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=771111","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2362932","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02049577","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v5","total_page":439,"paragraph_count":1658,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dABmy1":{"id":"GYL53dABmy1","type":"work","title":"滇行紀程","authors":[{"name":"許纘曾","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《滇行紀程》•一卷、《續鈔》•一卷，《東還紀程》•一卷、《續鈔》•一卷","author_info":"國朝許纘曾撰","summary":"國朝許纘曾撰。纘曾字孝修，號鶴沙，華亭人。順治己丑進士。官至雲南按察使。《滇行紀程》，其赴雲南時所作。《東還紀程》則自雲南歸途所作。皆述所見山川古跡，物產土風，大抵志乘所有也。","edition":"大學士英廉購進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"additional_works":[{"book_title":"續鈔","n_juan":1},{"book_title":"續鈔","n_juan":1}],"related_works":[{"id":"GYLt1Da32is","title":"東還紀程"}],"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=6317490","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02049538","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v4","total_page":93,"paragraph_count":78,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dwMiD5":{"id":"GYL53dwMiD5","type":"work","title":"漢雋","authors":[{"name":"林越","role":"撰","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《漢雋》•十卷","author_info":"宋林越撰","summary":"宋林越撰。案陳振孫《書錄解題》載此書，卷數與今相符，而注稱“括蒼林鉞”。《處州府志》亦載林鉞。此本則皆作林越，未詳孰是也。其書取《漢書》中古雅之字，分類排纂為五十篇。每篇即以篇首二字為名，亦間附原注。前有紹興壬午越《自序》，稱大可以詳其事，次可以玩其詞。然割裂字句，漫無端緒，而曰可詳其事，其說殊誇。後有延祐庚申袁桷重刻《跋》，稱《漢雋》之作，蓋為習宏博便利，斯為定論矣。","edition":"江蘇巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=198058","type":"text","details":"林鉞、呂元"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=304017","type":"text","details":"林鉞、呂元"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=802743","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishierhuijilvshi","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY2107","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆十二年(1584)會稽呂氏刻本","version":"v17","total_page":411,"paragraph_count":1895,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-mingwanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ8921112209281","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"明萬曆刻本","version":"v1","total_page":512,"paragraph_count":3493,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dLCC7q":{"id":"GYL53dLCC7q","type":"work","title":"東游紀略","authors":[{"name":"張體乾","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《東游紀略》•二卷","author_info":"國朝張體乾撰","summary":"國朝張體乾撰。體乾字確齋，浮山人，官刑部郎中。是編乃其家居時自山西、河南東游泰山，往來紀行之作。逐日記載見聞，於古跡頗有考訂。途中吟詠二百餘首，亦即附於逐日之後。其詩規仿白、陸，時亦具體。","comment":"──右“傳記類”雜錄之屬，五十八部、一百一十二卷，皆附《存目》。","edition":"鴻臚寺少卿曹學閔家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2077029","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02049540","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v2","total_page":172,"paragraph_count":1268,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-qingqianlongkeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NLG312001072425","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"清乾隆26年[1761]刻本","version":"v1","total_page":176,"paragraph_count":209,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dZAaqM":{"id":"GYL53dZAaqM","type":"work","title":"劉豫事蹟","authors":[{"name":"曹溶","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《劉豫事蹟》•一卷","author_info":"國朝曹溶撰","summary":"國朝曹溶撰。溶有《崇禎五十宰相傳》，已著錄。是書本楊克弼《偽豫傳》，又雜采他書附益之，視原《傳》所述較詳。","comment":"──右“傳記類”別錄之屬，六部、八卷，皆附《存目》。","additional_comment":"（案：以上皆逆亂之人，自為一傳者。命曰《別錄》，示不與諸傳比也。其割據僣竊之雄，別附《載記》。征討削平之事，別入《雜史》。均不與此同科。）","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=125113","type":"text"}]},"GYL53dQW6QX":{"id":"GYL53dQW6QX","type":"work","title":"張邦昌事略","authors":[{"name":"王稱","role":"撰","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《張邦昌事略》•一卷","author_info":"舊本題宋王稱撰","summary":"舊本題宋王稱撰。核其文，即《東都事略•僣偽傳》也。摘其一卷，別立名目，又改“王偁”為“王稱”，可謂愈偽愈拙。曹溶收之《學海類編》，蓋偶未考也。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=429687","type":"text"}]},"GYL53dUrgYf":{"id":"GYL53dUrgYf","type":"work","title":"徐海本末","authors":[{"name":"茅坤","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《徐海本末》•一卷","author_info":"明茅坤撰","summary":"明茅坤撰。坤字順甫，歸安人，嘉靖戊戌進士，官至大名兵備副使，事蹟具《明史•文苑傳》。坤好談兵，罷官後值倭事方急，嘗為胡宗憲招入幕，與共籌兵計。此編乃紀宗憲誘誅寇首徐海之事。皆所親見，故敍述特詳，與史所載亦多相合。袁褧以此書與《汪直傳》合刻入《金聲玉振集》中，題曰《海寇後編》。今析出各著於錄焉。","edition":"戶部尚書王際華家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1}},"GYL53d5qBps":{"id":"GYL53d5qBps","type":"work","title":"塞北小鈔","authors":[{"name":"高士奇","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《塞北小鈔》•一卷","author_info":"國朝高士奇撰","summary":"國朝高士奇撰。士奇有《春秋地名考略》，已著錄。是書乃康熙癸亥六月癸未士奇扈從聖駕北巡，會士奇遘疾，行至鞍匠屯而返。記其途中恩遇及往來所經，以成是編。自鞍匠屯以後，駐蹕之地，仍案日恭載。至閏六月丁酉回鑾，宣示塞外，所得盤羊、夜光木諸事，亦並錄焉。《自序》稱奉職七年，巡幸所至，各有紀錄，次第成編。而上所諮詢以及恩遇之隆，則慎而不書。偶檢明金幼孜《北征錄》，見其凡有賜予，纖悉必載，亦不忘君恩之意。故是編載錫賚顧問，比他記特為詳悉。至所考塞外古跡，以今核之，多不甚確。如以喇嘛洞為臥如來館之類，尤涉附會。蓋身所未經，而僅據明以前人之典籍，宜其依稀影響爾。","edition":"大學士英廉購進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"shidianguji-kangxijiankeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NLG312001059422","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"康熙間刻本","version":"v1","total_page":48,"paragraph_count":486,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dSgPUb":{"id":"GYL53dSgPUb","type":"work","title":"偽豫傳","authors":[{"name":"楊克弼","role":"撰","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《偽豫傳》•一卷","author_info":"宋楊克弼撰","summary":"宋楊克弼撰。述劉豫降金，僣號始末。其《序》稱以豫逆臣，不當稱偽齊，故削其國號而名稱之，以示貶也。《傳》中載豫阜昌八年，遣宣義郎楊克弼乞師大金，克弼他辭，乃改差韓元美。是克弼亦嘗仕豫，豫廢後乃複歸宋耳。陳振孫《書錄解題》作《逆臣劉豫傳》，楊堯弼、楊載等撰，與此本不同。“克”、“堯”字形相近，未知孰是也。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1}},"GYL53dCKPBd":{"id":"GYL53dCKPBd","type":"work","title":"南征紀程","authors":[{"name":"黃叔璥","role":"撰","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《南征紀程》•一卷","author_info":"國朝黃叔璥撰","summary":"國朝黃叔璥撰。叔璥號玉圃，大興人，康熙己丑進士，官至常鎮揚通道。是編乃其為監察御史時巡視臺灣，自京師至閩所記。始於康熙後壬寅正月，而迄於是年六月，分日紀載。","edition":"編修勵守謙家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1}},"GYL53deAnum":{"id":"GYL53deAnum","type":"work","title":"通鑒總類","authors":[{"name":"沈樞","role":"撰","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《通鑒總類》•二十卷","author_info":"宋沈樞撰","summary":"宋沈樞撰。樞字持要，德清人，紹興間進士，官至太子詹事、光祿卿，諡憲敏。是書乃其致仕時所編。取司馬光《資治通鑒》事蹟，仿《冊府元龜》之例，分為二百七十一門。每門各以事標題，略依時代前後為次，亦間採光《議論》附之。所分門目，頗有繁碎。如《賞罰》門外又立《貶責》、《功賞》二門，《外戚》門外又立《貴戚》一門，《近習》門外又立《寵倖》一門，《隱逸》門外又立《高尚》一門，《積善》門外又立《陰德》一門者，不一而足。又如安重榮奏請逾分不過驕蹇，乃以此一條別立《僣竊》一門，則配隸不確。東周下迄五代，興廢不一，乃獨取申徹論燕必亡、黃泓論燕必複二條，立為《興廢》一門，則疏漏太甚。然《通鑒》浩博，猝難盡覽。司馬光嘗言惟王勝之曾讀一過，餘人不能數卷即已倦睡。則采摭精華，區分事類，使考古者易於檢錄。其書雖陋，亦不妨過而存之也。嘉定中鋟版潮陽，樓鑰嘗為之序。元至正中浙江行省重刊，周伯琦又序之。二人皆博物君子，而肯以文章弁其首，殆以操觚數典，尚有一壺千金之用歟。","edition":"安徽巡撫采進本"}],"books":["CXVzssZuZzw"],"juan_count":{"number":20},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=74891","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=793151","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-sikuquanshuben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/SK0938","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"四庫全書本","version":"v5","total_page":3933,"paragraph_count":6108,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-sunlongmingwanlikebe","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ89241199902327015750","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"孫隆明萬曆23年刻本","version":"v2","total_page":2926,"paragraph_count":7954,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-sunlongmingwanlikebe-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ89241199902227614640","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"孫隆明萬曆23年刻本","version":"v2","total_page":2926,"paragraph_count":7558,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53dNKoLT":{"id":"GYL53dNKoLT","type":"work","title":"安祿山事蹟","authors":[{"name":"姚汝能","role":"撰","dynasty":"唐"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《安祿山事蹟》•三卷","author_info":"唐姚汝能撰","summary":"唐姚汝能撰。汝能始末未詳。陳振孫《書錄解題》稱其官華陰縣尉，未詳裏居。則宋時已無可考矣。是書上卷序祿山始生，至玄宗寵遇，起長安三年，盡天寶十二載事。中卷序天寶十三四載祿山構亂事。下卷序祿山僣號被殺，並安慶緒、史思明、史朝義事。下盡寶應元年，記述頗詳。世所傳祿山《櫻桃詩》，即出此書。葉夢得《避暑錄話》嘗摭以為笑。其瑣雜可知矣。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=619273","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=801092","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=901637","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02084557","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v5","total_page":96,"paragraph_count":88,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-xuantongeryinmoushib","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL01024744","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"宣統二年陰繆氏本","version":"v5","total_page":79,"paragraph_count":120,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-xuehaileibian","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CXHLB041","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"學海類編","version":"v4","total_page":110,"paragraph_count":70,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53drMW8f":{"id":"GYL53drMW8f","type":"work","title":"東漢精華","authors":[{"name":"呂祖謙","role":"撰","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《東漢精華》•十四卷","author_info":"宋呂祖謙撰","summary":"宋呂祖謙撰。是編乃其《兩漢精華》之一。即範氏之書摘其要語而論之，或比類以明之。於光武、明、章、和四帝《紀》尤為詳悉。所略者惟《表》、《志》耳。然不具事之始末，所論每條僅一二語，略抒大意，亦不申其所以然。蓋是書乃閱史之時摘錄於冊，以備文章議論之用。後人重祖謙之名，因而刊之。與洪邁《經史法語》均非有意著書者也。","edition":"衍聖公孔昭煥家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":14}},"GYL53dHyDCK":{"id":"GYL53dHyDCK","type":"work","title":"念貽剩紀","authors":[{"name":"周宣智","role":"編","dynasty":"清"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《念貽剩紀》•一卷","author_info":"國朝周宣智編","summary":"國朝周宣智編。宣智自號鏡亭老人，長沙人。初，張獻忠躪湖廣時，宣智曾祖繼聖，聚鄉勇自守。獻忠招授偽官，繼聖不從，劫系其母馬氏、妻吳氏及其弟繼珩妻陳氏、繼隨妻項氏以脅之，馬氏及三婦皆罵賊死。繼聖亦被斷腕後潛逃以免，卒伺隙破賊複讎。湖廣總督何騰蛟上其功，授教授。事載《湖廣通志》中。乾隆壬午，宣智裒其行狀墓銘之類，共為一編，而以繼聖遺詩十二首附焉。","edition":"侍講劉亨地家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1}},"GYL53djAzzB":{"id":"GYL53djAzzB","type":"work","title":"史記法語","authors":[{"name":"洪邁","role":"編","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《史記法語》•八卷","author_info":"宋洪邁編","summary":"宋洪邁編。邁字景盧，鄱陽人，紹興乙丑中博學鴻詞科，官至端明殿學士，諡文敏，事蹟具《宋史》本傳。是編於《史記》百三十篇內，自二字以上，句法古雋者，依次標出，亦間錄舊注。蓋與《經子法語》等編同以備修詞之用。《書錄解題》載之《類書類》，稱十八卷。此本乃止八卷，似非完書。然卷末有題識一行雲：“淳熙十二年二月刊於婺州。”是當時刊本實止八卷，《書錄題解》所載，衍一“十”字明矣。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":8},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=723972","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-chaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02049543","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"抄本","version":"v3","total_page":267,"paragraph_count":1732,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL53doUuGs":{"id":"GYL53doUuGs","type":"work","title":"十七史詳節","authors":[{"name":"呂祖謙","role":"編","dynasty":"宋"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《十七史詳節》•二百七十三卷","author_info":"宋呂祖謙編","summary":"宋呂祖謙編。祖謙有《古周易》，已著錄。此蓋其讀史時刪節備檢之本，而建陽書坊為刻而傳之者。凡《史記》二十卷、《西漢書》三十卷、《東漢書》三十卷、《三國志》二十卷、《晉書》三十卷，《南史》二十五卷、《北史》二十八卷、《隋書》二十卷、《唐書》六十卷、《五代史》十卷。前冠以《疆理》、《世系》、《紀年》之圖。所錄大抵隨時節抄，不必盡出精要。如《東漢》、《晉》二史內，四言讚語，於本書已屬贅拇駢枝，乃一概摘存，殊為冗雜。又如《北史》紀傳為隋代而作者，業已併入《隋書》，乃獨《四夷》一傳仍及隋事，而《隋書》內遂刪去之，為例亦間有不純。然南宋諸儒，大抵研究性命，而輕視史學。故朱子作《貢舉私議》，欲分年試士，以《史記》、《兩漢》為一科，《三國》、《晉書》、《南北史》為一科，《新舊唐書》、《五代史》為一科。蓋虛談無實之弊，朱子亦深慮之矣。祖謙雖亦從事於講學，而淹通典籍，不肯借程子玩物喪志之說，以文飾空疏。故朱子稱其史學分外仔細。附存其目，俾儒者知前人讀書，必貫徹首尾。即所刪節之本，而用功之深至，可以概見。則此二百七十三卷者，雖不能盡諸史之全，而足以為宋儒不廢史學之明證也。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":273},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=6732009","type":"text"}]}}